        <div class="review-title-text">The morning depuff is real</div>
        <p class="review-text">I wake up puffy every morning no matter how much water I drink. Five minutes with this stone and my face looks completely different. I keep it in the fridge for extra cooling. The amethyst is gorgeous and feels so solid.</p>
        <div class="review-author">Megan L. <span class="review-badge">Verified Buyer</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="review-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
        <div class="review-title-text">Better than the jade one I had before</div>
        <p class="review-text">I had a jade gua sha for 2 years and the difference is night and day. The amethyst is smoother, heavier, and feels way more premium. The edges fit perfectly along my jawline. Already ordered one for my sister.</p>
        <div class="review-author">Nicole R. <span class="review-badge">Verified Buyer</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="review-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
        <div class="review-title-text">People keep asking what I changed</div>
        <p class="review-text">I've been using this every morning for about 3 weeks now. Two coworkers asked if I lost weight and my mom said I look rested. I haven't changed anything else in my routine. The gua sha is the only new thing.</p>
        <div class="review-author">Jennifer K. <span class="review-badge">Verified Buyer</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="review-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
        <div class="review-title-text">It's so relaxing I almost fall back asleep</div>
        <p class="review-text">The cool stone on my face in the morning is genuinely the best part of my day. My under-eyes look less puffy and my face shape looks more defined. The technique guide helped a lot because I had no idea what I was doing before.</p>
        <div class="review-author">Priya S. <span class="review-badge">Verified Buyer</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="review-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9734;</div>
